\c 17
\s Abantwana bakoIsrayeli basola uMozisi ngamanzi
\p
\v 1 Inhlangano yonke yabantwana bakoIsrayeli yasuka enkangala yeSini\x + 16.1. Nani 33.12,14.\x*, ngamalombolombo abo, ngokomlayo weN\nd kosi\nd*, bamisa inkamba eRefidimi; kodwa kwakungelamanzi okuthi abantu banathe.
\v 2 Ngakho abantu bamsola uMozisi bathi: Sinike amanzi, sinathe\x + Nani 20.3,4.\x*. UMozisi wasesithi kubo: Lingisolelani? Liyilingelani iN\nd kosi\x + Dute. 6.16. Hlab. 78.18,41; 95.8. Isa. 7.12. Mat. 4.7. 1 Kor. 10.9. Heb. 3.8.\x*\nd*?
\v 3 Abantu basebesomela amanzi lapho, abantu bangunguna kuMozisi\x + 15.24; 16.2.\x* bathi: Wasenyuselani eGibhithe ukuze usibulale thina labantwana bethu lezifuyo zethu ngokoma?
\v 4 UMozisi wasekhala eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + 14.15.\x* esithi: Ngizakwenzani kulababantu? Sekukancane ukuthi bangikhande ngamatshe\x + 1 Sam. 30.6. Joha. 8.59; 10.31-33.\x*.
\v 5 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuMozisi: Dlula phambi kwabantu, uthathe kanye lawe kubadala bakoIsrayeli, lentonga yakho owatshaya\x + 7.20. Nani 20.8.\x* umfula ngayo\x + 2.3; 7.20.\x*, ithathe ngesandla sakho, uhambe.
\v 6 Khangela, ngizakuma lapho phambi kwakho phezu kwedwala eHorebe; njalo uzatshaya idwala, kuphume-ke kulo amanzi ukuze abantu banathe\x + Nani 20.10,11. Hlab. 78.15,16,20; 105.41; 114.8. 1 Kor. 10.4.\x*. UMozisi wasesenza njalo phambi kwamehlo abadala bakoIsrayeli.
\v 7 Wasebiza ibizo lendawo \add ngokuthi\add* yiMasa lo\add kuthi\add* yiMeriba\x + Nani 20.13. Hlab. 81.7.\x* ngenxa yokusola kwabantwana bakoIsrayeli langenxa yokuyilinga kwabo iN\nd kosi\nd* besithi: IN\nd kosi\nd* iphakathi kwethu yini loba hatshi?
\s Ukulwa kwabo loAmaleki
\p
\v 8 Kwasekufika uAmaleki, walwa loIsrayeli eRefidimi.\x + Gen. 36.12. Nani 24.20. Dute. 25.17. 1 Sam. 15.2.\x*
\v 9 UMozisi wasesithi kuJoshuwa\x + Seb. 7.45. Heb. 4.8.\x*: Sikhethele amadoda, uphume uyekulwa loAmaleki; kusasa ngizakuma engqongeni yoqaqa, lentonga kaNkulunkulu izakuba sesandleni sami\x + 4.2,4,20.\x*.
\v 10 UJoshuwa wasesenza njengokutsho kukaMozisi kuye, walwa loAmaleki. OMozisi, uAroni loHuri basebesenyukela engqongeni yoqaqa.
\v 11 Kwasekusithi lapho uMozisi ephakamisa isandla sakhe, uIsrayeli waba lamandla; kodwa lapho wehlisa isandla sakhe, uAmaleki waba lamandla.
\v 12 Kodwa izandla zikaMozisi zaba nzima, ngakho bathatha ilitshe, balibeka ngaphansi kwakhe, ukuthi ahlale kulo. OAroni loHuri basebesekela izandla zakhe, omunye engapha lomunye engale, ukuze izandla zakhe ziqine lize litshone ilanga.
\v 13 UJoshuwa wasemchitha uAmaleki labantu bakhe ngobukhali benkemba.
\p
\v 14 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuMozisi: Bhala\x + 34.27.\x* lokhu egwalweni kube yisikhumbuzo, ukubeke ezindlebeni zikaJoshuwa ukuthi ngokwesula ngizakwesula ukukhunjulwa kukaAmaleki ngaphansi kwamazulu\x + Nani 24.20. Dute. 25.19. 1 Sam. 15.3,7. 30.1,17. 2 Sam. 8.12.\x*.
\v 15 UMozisi wasesakha ilathi, wabiza ibizo lalo \add ngokuthi\add*: UJehova-nisi;
\v 16 wathi: Ngoba isandla sisesihlahleni sobukhosi seN\nd kosi\nd*, iN\nd kosi\nd* izakuba lempi imelene loAmaleki kusukela kusizukulwana kusiya kusizukulwana.